# SliderSpinBox Component

When adding a slider with an accompanying spinbox for precise value entry, use the reusable `SliderSpinBox` component at `scenes/ui/slider_spin_box.tscn`.

## Usage in .tscn

Instance the scene and set exported properties on the instance:

```
[ext_resource type="PackedScene" path="res://scenes/ui/slider_spin_box.tscn" id="slider_spin_id"]

[node name="MySliderSpin" parent="SomeRow" instance=ExtResource("slider_spin_id")]
unique_name_in_owner = true
layout_mode = 2
min_value = 0.1
max_value = 5.0
step = 0.01
value = 1.0
allow_greater = true
```

## Usage in GDScript

```gdscript
@onready var my_slider_spin: SliderSpinBox = %MySliderSpin

func _ready() -> void:
    my_slider_spin.value_changed.connect(_on_my_value_changed)

func _on_my_value_changed(value: float) -> void:
